show.description: Blossoms 2003 is an emotional fantasy drama that follows a father and daughter who discover a mysterious portal to the past. As they step into the year where everything went wrong, he is given a rare chance to confront his regrets, mend broken relationships, and rewrite the fate of his family. A tale of love, guilt, and redemption, where time becomes both a gift and a test.
